				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: The Taken King &amp; Patch 2.0
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1841300">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							A cool new feature in TTK is that many exotics are now rewarded from Quest Lines, or performing specific actions.  Players today found how to get one of the missing exotics, and the method it was discovered implies a whole method that needs to be tested.<br />
<br />
The New Exotic today was discovered by running a Heroic Mode of a Story Mission, except instead of going the primary direction, you board his Ketch, which initiates a timer to kill everything in under 10 minutes. If you win, it gives you a max level exotic sniper rifle, and a chance at a rare ship (and counts as completing the mission).<br />
<br />
Similarly, there are other hidden quest/events in the game.  My brother and I did one that awarded a shader (I think) and an Emblem, it required us to go to two different areas, and activate two consoles at the same time, which opened a door that lead to a giant Hive Knight we had to down.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
