							Yeah, the speaker gives some hints about it, but basically the City and Tower have a government and the Guardians are just a branch of that government.<br />
<br />
Pretty recently in history a group of Guardians did something everyone considered extreme and were exiled.  It appears that was when Guardians were exiled from the city after that incident, due to normal humans fearing <br />
<br />
<a href="http://destinytimeline.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://destinytimeline.com/</a>  Note that the timeline is kind of screwed up because that first section with the Krill/Hive, The Sky (Light), and The Deep (Darkness) happened <b>Billions</b> of years ago, not Thousands of years ago.
						</blockquote>
